I knew I was going to do that.

00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:02.670
Oceanography Research and
Education on the University

00:01:02.670 --> 00:01:04.470
of Hawaii's Manoa Campus.

00:01:04.470 --> 00:01:05.770
Please excuse me.

00:01:05.770 --> 00:01:10.740
I am an arts and sciences
major and I knew that,

00:01:10.740 --> 00:01:14.460
but we are so delighted to have
