00:13:33.340 --> 00:13:38.810
so to have the opener of a
program like this be the Library

00:13:38.810 --> 00:13:42.040
of Congress is for me higher
than having the President

00:13:42.040 --> 00:13:43.340
of the United States here.

00:13:43.340 --> 00:13:46.510
So, I want to a there.

