00:31:23.170 --> 00:31:26.430
of academic elites and
legal elites and so on,

00:31:26.430 --> 00:31:28.520
and then you flash-forward
to the present era

00:31:28.520 --> 00:31:31.420
and they're much more
concentrated in these sort,

00:31:31.420 --> 00:31:34.220
you know, the sort
of major East Coast

00:31:34.220 --> 00:31:36.150
and West Coast urban
centers and then sort

00:31:36.150 --> 00:31:38.620
