much stronger segregation

00:31:41.850 --> 00:31:45.330
by education in the U.S. than
you had 40 or 50 years ago

00:31:45.330 --> 00:31:48.390
and you have sort of fewer
local elites that are sort

00:31:48.390 --> 00:31:52.690
of in touch with, you know,
Iowa, New Hampshire or whatever,

00:31:52.690 --> 00:31:54.130
you know, whatever
state they come from

00:31:54.130 --> 00:31:57.670
and you have this nationally
elite that's less in touch

00:31:57.670 --> 00:32:00.550
