00:35:34.640 --> 00:35:38.880
I found over the
years in my long life,

00:35:38.880 --> 00:35:42.620
that you can tell a lot
about someone's world view

00:35:42.620 --> 00:35:46.990
by whether they think of
themselves as totally self-make

