01:27:08.140 --> 01:27:11.890
of the American dream
is this conversation

01:27:11.890 --> 01:27:16.720
that is never ending, tonight
true to the Kluge moto,

01:27:16.720 --> 01:27:18.910
"We've given you
a lot of thought,

01:27:18.910 --> 01:27:20.760
a lot of call to action."

